The tag submit/tizen_ivi_milestone/20131113.054009 was pushed, but it was not completed because of the following reason(s):

- The tag means you want to submit commit c0a3c5b934b997cf4bba32b3880a0b24f287bd12 in tizen_ivi_milestone branch to OBS, but this commit does NOT exist in tizen_ivi_milestone branch. Please use correct branch name as version in tag name submit/{version}/{date.time}.

Suggest to use "gbs submit" to trigger submission, or use following command to create tag "git tag submit/${version}/$(date --utc +%%Y%%m%%d.%%H%%M%%S) -m "****" ".
